==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ὁμοιόω / homoioō / hom-oy-o'-o
*From [[ὅμοιος]].

===Verb===
'''ὁμοιόω'''

# To [[assimilate]], that is, [[compare]]; passively to become similar: - be (make) [[like]], (in the) liken (-ess), [[resemble]].

